  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main purpose of this study is to assess the efficacy of early oseltamivir treatment
      (started within 24 hours of the onset of influenza symptoms) in preventing the development of
      acute otitis media as a complication of influenza in children aged 1-3 years.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
